似碰碰車禁，d 女人個袋可以亂撞，撞到我個春袋，好聲好氣禁講：唔好意思，你個袋撞到我下面，佢既反應可以係啤我。<br />\n認真我想死，到底人生有咩意義？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T15:57:51.000Z","msg":"咁不如刷下首抽，無左條撚咪可以狠狠打翻男人個無用春袋報仇囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39ac6937544c23009f5ab4bedc4ae3c0ecdd0df0","tid":833521,"uid":183111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9b631520dba51737b42a300b8e4296d9c3ac52d","tid":833521,"uid":204728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T15:52:21.000Z","msg":"一樣係Psycho JJ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一樣係Sen學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我而家係Year 2 同埋有語言障礙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n由小學到中學一直有接受言語治療<br />\n不過一直都無乜明顯嘅進步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T16:00:50.000Z","msg":"Sen 係呢個教育制度係好辛苦，你升到都好利害嫁啦，又唔似我又病又想死。你起碼冇生命危險啊。<br />\n我查過書，真係冇咩特別野幫到手，只知讀寫又細分唔同種。之前遇過專教sen 既老師，佢話sen 比平常人有創意，唔知係咪我地唔係用文字來思考既原故呢。"},{"pid":"e64ca717fba5253ff2a24c78a10e20b75135dab8","tid":833521,"uid":59328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da2ad8bf2333c37f7d2d8ab47a4a283e907c4a6d","tid":833521,"uid":183111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9cffd5e5eeba11bb7ee3f7dd7ee13e6d807554da","tid":833521,"uid":189646,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e9c4fd6bfd5767e4ee0874fa851337943d869ad7","tid":833521,"uid":183111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T14:59:03.000Z","msg":"人地上堂唔明既野我明，會問下我禁囉，不過有時都冇心機上堂，成績就自然嗎嗎"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T15:03:42.000Z","msg":"拎一二個人比？ 叻過你的人大把 ， 你自己唔努力 就賴，無人幫到你<br />\n世界好大 ，比你叻的人多的事<br />\n<br />\n但